The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-07-2013 THURS










The Glenn Beck Program




          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 11/7/13Thursday, November 07, 2013 12:02 PM






Glenn recaps the Country Music Awards 
   and the little musical surprise against Obamacare. 

 Also, young author Alley Breedlove joins the show to discuss her new book,
   When Will the Heaven Begin,
     the story about her young brother Ben who saw heaven,
       just before he died.  

   Plus, Ann Coulter joins the program to discuss the fall out from the recent elections
